== Description ==
Test Tools area is created with the aim of building the framework needed for system test development and execution. <br\><br\>

== Ericsson Lab ==
Continuous System Integration Test (CSIT) will be available at M5 and the test framework will be hosted in existing OpenDaylight servers.<br\><br\> 
In paralel we have a test environment in Ericsson Lab that can be used for:

* Get familiar with controller (DUT)
* Evaluate test tools
* Debug system test code
 
Following VMs are available:
 
* Test Tools
* Controller
* Mininet

